snippet.title: Plant Nursery Simulator | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
🌱 Wishlist on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3474700/Plant_Nursery_Simulator/

Run your own Plant Nursery in this relaxing sim. Grow, sell, and manage your shop while expanding with greenhouses and staff. A relaxing and cozy game for farming and simulation game fans!
